# Write a program to find out whether a student is pass or fail, if it requires total 40% and at at least 33% in each subject to pass. Assume 3 subject and take marks as an input from the user
# Let the 3 subject be physics, chemistry, maths

phy=float(input("Enter the marks of Physics:\n"))
chem=float(input("Enter the marks of Chemistry:\n"))
maths=float(input("Enter the marks of Maths:\n"))

p_percent=(phy/100)*100
c_percent=(chem/100)*100
m_percent=(maths/100)*100

avg=p_percent+c_percent+m_percent

if p_percent<33 or c_percent<33 or m_percent<33:
    print("sorry, as you have failed, you can't be promoted to next class")
elif avg>=40:
    print("Conratulations, you have passed in all 3 subjects and promoted to next class")

          
